rdEntryAmount,\n  determineWinnerFromRandomness as determineLordWinnerFromRandomness,\n  mapSlotToPlayer,\n  verifyLordRound,\n  calculateJackpotPayout,\n  type LordPlayerEntry,\n  type RoundSettledEvent,\n  type LordVerificationResult,\n}\n```\n\n### 3. Verification Module\n\n**No `verification.ts` exists** in the game-engine package. There is a `coinflip` module but not a shared `verification.ts` for the general pattern.\n\nThe Lord of the RNGs verification is self-contained in `lordofrngs.ts` and follows this pattern:\n- Event data is parsed from on-chain logs\n- Player list is reconstructed from round state\n- `verifyLordRound()` re-derives winner deterministically and checks against claimed values\n- Returns detailed result with errors if any check fails"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: af48f2b (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 30612\ntool_uses: 3\nduration_ms: 10071</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"460d6ed6-55a6-44c8-8f2f-a24854f1a42b","uuid":"5cf4a889-837d-457e-a426-9f15a70f14ee","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read the Lord of the RNGs verification functions in the game-engine package. I need:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/lordofrngs.ts` - particularly the `verifyLordRound`, `RoundSettledEvent`, `LordVerificationResult` types\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/index.ts` - to see what's exported\n3. Also check `sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/verification.ts` if it exists (coinflip verification pattern)\n\nRead these files fully and report their contents.","agentId":"af48f2b","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have the contents of the two main files. The third file (`verification.ts`) doesn't exist in the game-engine package. Here's what I found:\n\n## File Contents Report\n\n### 1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/lordofrngs.ts`\n\n**Key Types:**\n- **`RoundSettledEvent`** (lines 49-59): Interface containing:\n  - `tier: number`\n  - `roundNumber: bigint`\n  - `winner: PublicKey`\n  - `randomness: Uint8Array` (32 bytes)\n  - `winningSlot: number`\n  - `totalEntries: number`\n  - `payoutAmount: bigint`\n  - `feeAmount: bigint`\n  - `vrfRequestKey: PublicKey`\n\n- **`LordVerificationResult`** (lines 62-67): Interface with:\n  - `valid: boolean`\n  - `errors: string[]`\n  - `computedWinningSlot?: number`\n  - `computedWinner?: PublicKey`\n\n**Key Functions:**\n- **`verifyLordRound(event, players)`** (lines 140-185): Main verification function that:\n  1. Re-derives winning slot from randomness\n  2. Verifies winning slot matches\n  3. Verifies winner matches\n  4. Verifies fee equals 3% of total pool\n  5. Returns `LordVerificationResult`\n\n- **`determineWinnerFromRandomness(randomness, totalEntries, players)`** (lines 82-90): Maps VRF randomness to winner\n- **`deriveWinningSlot(randomness, totalEntries)`** (lines 96-104): Converts first 8 bytes of randomness (little-endian u64) to slot via modulo\n- **`mapSlotToPlayer(winningSlot, players)`** (lines 111-126): Maps slot index to player based on contiguous entry ranges\n- **`calculateJackpotPayout(tier, totalEntries)`** (lines 190-198): Calculates payout as pool × 0.97 (3% fee)\n\n### 2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/index.ts`\n\n**Exports from lordofrngs module** (lines 60-73):\n```typescript\nexport {\n  LORDOFRNGS_PROGRAM_ID,\n  getRoundPda,\n  getConfigPda as getLordConfigPda,\n  getLordEntryAmount,\n  determineWinnerFromRandomness as determineLordWinnerFromRandomness,\n  mapSlotToPlayer,\n  verifyLordRound,\n  calculateJackpotPayout,\n  type LordPlayerEntry,\n  type RoundSettledEvent,\n  type LordVerificationResult,\n}\n```\n\n### 3. Verification Module\n\n**No `verification.ts` exists** in the game-engine package. There is a `coinflip` module but not a shared `verification.ts` for the general pattern.\n\nThe Lord of the RNGs verification is self-contained in